window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>This CHRONOS Files short story appeared originally in </b><b><i>CLONES: The Anthology</i></b><b> </b></p> <p>A familiar blip of green light in the corner of his room has Kiernan Dunne hoping the new arrival is Kate, so that he can abandon the rescue he's planning. But the time traveler who just blinked in is a future version of Kiernan, and judging from the number scrawled on his forehead, he's not the only copy.</p>"; 
